metadata.description: Northpointe Bancshares, Inc. operates as the bank holding company for Northpointe Bank provides various banking products and services. It offers noninterest-bearing accounts, savings, money-market demand accounts, and certificates of deposits; personal and business banking, kids saving, and health saving accounts; home loans; and mortgage purchase program. The company was incorporated in 1998 and is headquartered in Grand Rapids, Michigan.
